headline: U.S. Bank Shield™ Visa® Card offers 0% intro APR for 24 billing cycles
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 17, 2025--U.S. Bank, a leading provider of payment services and solutions, today announced a new consumer credit card to complement its growing portfolio of payment products for consumer and business banking clients: the U.S. Bank Shield™ Visa® Card.

headline: Tracking Ole Andreas Halvorsen's Viking Global Portfolio - Q4 2024 Update
summary: Viking Global's 13F stock portfolio increased from $27.44B to $30.90B, with holdings rising from 83 to 86. Read more to see the portfolio's Q4 2024 review.
